00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:52,520
You don't have to think very deeply.

287
00:11:53,300 --> 00:11:53,860
What's that?

288
00:11:55,420 --> 00:11:55,880
Yeah,

289
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:56,820
we'll have to do theta too.

290
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,380
We've only done r up till now.

291
00:11:58,380 --> 00:11:58,700
Yes?

292
00:11:59,040 --> 00:12:00,460
What do you really mean when

293
00:12:00,460 --> 00:12:01,880
you say it's not a real force?

294
00:12:02,580 --> 00:12:03,040
Well,

295
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:04,400
by definition...

296
00:12:09,859 --> 00:12:12,440
I constantly say this over and over again.

297
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,420
But then I slip into the same pattern.

298
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:18,160
I'm always telling young physicists and old physicists,

